item.title: 200 kVA Ultra Quiet Fusteq Generator
item.dc:creator: hadimarashy
item.description:
Another range of 200kVA generators that have been built to the John F Hunt specification. These power units provide the same high levels of strength as the silenced range but are fitted with a special canopy to lower the noise even further. These 200 kVA generators provide the perfect solution in noise sensitive work and sit alongside our “Pink” sets as an alternative “silenced” solution.
Download Spec sheet

The post 200 kVA Ultra Quiet Fusteq Generator appeared first on Power.
